{"tid":622401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"20歲仔遊樂場遇襲 遭4惡煞鐵通扑頭","createTime":"2018-04-09T06:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T13:27:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"09cc8ac35e8fe23f1b1a8dca8ed62f2961f0a644","tid":622401,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T06:24:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180409/20356491\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180409%2F20356491&d=zzcAzgRpBJJpPIykeAO1UwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=211cc3db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180409%2F20356491&h=6371c16a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180409/20356491</a><br />\n<br />\n20歲仔遊樂場遇襲<br />\n遭4惡煞鐵通扑頭<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】土瓜灣發生傷人案。昨晚近10時，一名20歲姓李男子在土瓜灣遊樂場內，遭4名兇徒持鐵通襲擊，受傷倒地，兇徒逞兇後即逃去。救護員其後到場，把男事主送院治理。現場所見男傷者血流披面，躺在擔架床上送院，其間更需要戴上頸箍。警方正調查案件，追緝兇徒歸案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，男事主曾在遊樂場近球場附近與人爭執，其間遭對方最少4人追打。他一直逃跑，惟跑至遊樂場近長寧街的出口時，終被對方追上施襲。據知，兇徒包括南亞裔人士。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方事後封鎖現場調查，並在遊樂場內一體育館外的大樹下，撿獲一支約2呎半長鐵通，疑與案有關。警員亦曾在遊樂場範圍截停4名南亞裔人士調查，惟經調查後相信他們並非涉案兇徒。"},{"pid":"3e7f1cfd3135b969e0588e678a8ad12a3ce396d8","tid":622401,"uid":36857,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T08:10:14.000Z","msg":"張超雄又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18115500d2d0ae7ffb7f4b50696dd7191ee87101","tid":622401,"uid":116364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T08:16:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45189441ab28933c7cbadc76a0eaa755a7a86865","tid":622401,"uid":55488,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T08:18:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"640933f39537bfc077e9ca028d49283eff089784","tid":622401,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T08:18:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae92edbc67b0bd72c2214fccc1f7e19f96badb5a","tid":622401,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T10:14:39.000Z","msg":"玩下姐<br />\n郁d報公安做乜"},{"pid":"beb5257b32da910ef81315a38f02c5f03184d2eb","tid":622401,"uid":23697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T12:48:33.000Z","msg":"南亞人好無辜"},{"pid":"835bc18ce8399a38f5cf802b4f229bba11e786cb","tid":622401,"uid":51590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T12:54:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">多謝難民之父張超雄</span></span>"},{"pid":"3662c5f2c69a504560424eb78146d08e9f6ad6ec","tid":622401,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T12:54:57.000Z","msg":"硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef2c232784df68d3f1fbe4336f1bab0827b2b8b9","tid":622401,"uid":102096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T13:27:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}